{"tid":1901704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭家麒指警員不應加薪　梁美芬稱其他政府部門亦有不足","createTime":"2020-02-28T03:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T05:39:22.000Z","uid":152476,"like":59,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"381fac273ac6d67e4d0871119dbf13642b4ef672","tid":1901704,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"拉其他部門落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會財委會繼續審議公務員加薪撥款申請，討論議員許智峯上次會議提出的中止待續動議。公民黨郭家麒說，支持有關動議，他指出，很多市民給予警察零分，警方過去一直暴力對待市民，因此警員不應獲得加薪，形容「一毫字都可以加」。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯梁美芬說反對中止動議，指其他政府部門亦有不足，例如食環署未有完全清除抹黑性的單張，香港電台刺激仇恨，認為不應因個別警員表現不佳，就將堅守崗位的公務員救命錢取走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511396-20200228.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511396-20200228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0TIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=75fb7b89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511396-20200228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=02523555\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511396-20200228.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"bf0ff5655ad4c5c0c92d1edfc1c583d80731ac81","tid":1901704,"uid":185628,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:23:40.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"532199cce298dda9dc2ad761cb5d4666e8afc669","tid":1901704,"uid":83582,"like":201,"dislike":4,"score":197,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:24:10.000Z","msg":"咁全部都唔好加就公平啦"},{"pid":"065100473363db4e4032c93565b6ebf782a88b1f","tid":1901704,"uid":68598,"like":87,"dislike":2,"score":85,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:24:13.000Z","msg":"咁梁美芬指邊埋邊個部門不足啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再果個部門唔好加囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31b5caeed881859427633304de7835b40d0361e","tid":1901704,"